Interface ICsvByteLineParser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseCsvByteLineParser, BaseCsvLineParser, BasicCsvByteLineParserExtended, BasicCsvLineParser, BasicCsvLineParserExtended, StandardCsvLineParser

    public interface ICsvByteLineParser
    Interface describing a CSV line parser - A class to break a line into the fields using a field-Seperator String

    Bruce Martin
